sources.title: The two pieces of 90 / I due pezzi da 90 (1971) Franco Franchi, Ciccio Ingrassia | Movie, Subtitles
sources.description:
Franco and Ciccio are forced to abandon their sausage factory to reach the godfather of Franco: Nico Cavallaro. The two do not know that he is a smuggler of drugs and wants them to transport the goods.

Italian audio subtitled in more than 30 languages. Make your choice in the video settings ⚙️

Director: Osvaldo Civirani
Stars: Franco Franchi, Ciccio Ingrassia, Margaret Rose Keil, & Carla Mancini
Genre: Italian film, Comedy
Original title: I due pezzi da 90
